<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.5">
<l>aṭuttārt teḻuntāḷ pilavāyviṭ</l>
<l>ṭalaṟa vavaḷmūk kayilvāḷāl</l>
<l>viṭuttāṉ viḷaṅku cuṭarāḻi</l>
<l>viṇṇōr perumāṉ naṇṇārmuṉ</l>
<l>kaṭuttārt teḻunta perumaḻaiyaik</l>
<l>kalloṉ ṟēnti yiṉaniraikkāt</l>
<l>taṭuttāṉ taṭaṅcūḻn taḻakāya</l>
<l>cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge in Śālagrāma which is beautiful, surrounded by ponds,</l>
<l rend="indent">of him who cut with a sharp sword her nose</l>
<l>So that she screamed, opening her cavernous mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">she who rose up, rushing and roaring,</l>
<l>The celestials’ lord with a bright, fiery discus, the one who,</l>
<l rend="indent">protecting the herd cattle,</l>
<l>Raising a mountain in front of his foe, blocked the rain</l>
<l rend="indent">which appeared, swift and roaring.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
